"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2402124\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2402124&d=2uC3t%2Br9CkjFZ%2FF5riHAvb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=0b873cf0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2402124&h=739cf91c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2402124</a>"},{"pid":"adbc6b57f4cac36f0760311e8ee614f65d91848c","tid":634960,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T00:07:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70614e63b904096d8acbf7a7f51cf58e7d3cd87a","tid":634960,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T00:54:28.000Z","msg":"samsung新機個壓感筆系統幾堅<br />\n<br />\n華為根本無資格貼住三星開價"},{"pid":"823e923b1fa1897f3d3efd8d6faeab60d69c9a6c","tid":634960,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T03:12:57.000Z","msg":"好似話去左慶恭宴，慶祝中興收皮"}]}